			<h4><a id="comment_link_64483175" name="comment_link_64483175" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23327641&amp;cid=64483175" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64483175)" >Re: This isn't how to end burning coal.</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64483175" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64483175); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
